{"tid":1996260,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"蘋果是全世界最貴的報紙 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-04-30T23:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T02:54:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a852f1823f85ef054ab3b88ad4325d692703638b","tid":1996260,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T23:40:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200501/20910040/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200501%2F20910040%2F&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rIVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=843e8c4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200501%2F20910040%2F&h=7c0156c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200501/20910040/</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果是全世界最貴的報紙 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200501/large/1588238005_a8d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200501%2Flarge%2F1588238005_a8d4.jpg&h=881479c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前天，Loser大聯盟總舵主、《蘋果日報》最癡心讀者梁振英在Facebook說：「今天的蘋果日報扣除馬經、體育、娛樂之後，只有5張所謂『新聞』（包括財經），我8秒鐘睇完，以8秒鐘花十元計算，一小時的消費是多少？答案是4500元，因此蘋果是全世界最貴的報紙。香港人是與有榮焉還是恥與為伍？」<br />\n<br />\n梁振英又講大話。蘋果除了馬經、體育、娛樂和包括財經的5張新聞，還有副刊。難道副刊已搞「副獨」，是蘋果可以分離的一部分？梁振英。。。他在Facebook響應本欄呼籲，把拙文〈寫給未訂閱蘋果的香港人〉一字不漏轉載，平日亦多次洋洋自得評論名采版文章，鐵證如山不容抵賴。梁振英說8秒鐘看完新聞，卻不說花多少時間啃副刊，這種情操不夠高尚。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英貌似揶揄蘋果，實則令無人看的左報躺着也中槍。我家樓下管理處，天天有疊空虛寂寞凍的《大公報》免費派發。。。。。梁振英講得真好！<br />\n<br />\n當然，「蘋果是全世界最貴的報紙」這說法，我是認同的。蘋果之貴不在價錢，而在價值。蘋果還不是香港唯一拒絕中共的媒體，但肯定是香港「言論自由」和「多元聲音」的代表符號。沒有壹傳媒，誰踢爆警務處助理處長陶輝（Rupert Dover）非法居住牌照屋、霸佔官地的醜聞？沒有壹傳媒，誰派記者。。。。令他窘得要像屯門公園大媽一樣躲到公廁？沒有壹傳媒，誰公開鄭月娥那份呈交中央，聲稱要利用疫情翻盤的。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n肥佬黎蝕到入肉都繼續做，正是為了守護「多元」和「自由」兩大無比珍貴的香港核心價值。中國大陸既無「自由」，亦無「多元」，在今天這個急速大陸化的香港，蘋果當然是全世界最貴的報紙了。「物以罕為貴」，連五歲小童也聽過吧？ <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾<br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com"},{"pid":"f7a200ea508a88d90f8f02db9c8a386f362743cf","tid":1996260,"uid":321977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T23:51:50.000Z","msg":"啱，自由你估免費？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e49000f8cdeaa407c53a5157446ed22dbf126fe","tid":1996260,"uid":201828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T23:55:34.000Z","msg":"自由從來係最貴嘅嘢，<br />\n活喺極權底下嘅奴才係無辦法想象，唔好怪佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bfdbdffbc2e89771bb9c4b3c4e0036d0b49e9d","tid":1996260,"uid":189157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T23:57:15.000Z","msg":"自由係最貴嘅野"},{"pid":"634d7267a7fcc5ec13a091c3ea39f5c867586d71","tid":1996260,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T23:58:54.000Z","msg":"果然識得拎大公報嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n689正宗豬隊友"},{"pid":"3bb0fd4a835bf5955a3f2192b5ce3284a8b2ffc4","tid":1996260,"uid":60131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T00:05:24.000Z","msg":"一分錢一分貨嘅嘢，689識鬼咩<br />\n過氣廢老返去睇太公報啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>巴絲們快啲訂蘋果喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"49c92173563c8a3ec00b775cbfed548ea5a8d646","tid":1996260,"uid":268857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a852f1823f85ef054ab3b88ad4325d692703638b","tid":1996260,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T23:40:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9